---
title: Cheesy BBQ Beyond Meat® Bowls with Buttery Charred Corn and Rice
description: Bowls are perfect for quick weekday meals and this one will be a hit with the whole family! Beyond Meat® is tossed in BBQ sauce, then spooned over buttery rice. Charred corn adds some extra comfort to this bowl!
